&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following people use the Iteration Plan:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The &lt;b>project manager&lt;/b>, to plan the iteration tasks, to schedule resource needs, and to track progress against&#xD;
        the schedule.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;b>Project team members&lt;/b>, to understand what they need to do, when they need to do it, and what other activities&#xD;
        they are dependent upon.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></purpose>
